column.name: REPORT_NAME
column.value: Example - Partners per Migration Status in Wave 1

column.name: CUSTOM_SQL
column.value: SELECT COUNT (*) AS Y, REPLACE( COALESCE (P.PARAM_VALUE, ''), '_', ' ') AS X FROM STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS P WHERE P.PARAM_NAME = 'Wave' AND P.PARAM_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND P.PARAM_VALUE != '' GROUP BY P.PARAM_VALUE ORDER BY 2

column.name: GRAPH_LABEL
column.value: Partners per Migration Status in Wave 1

column.name: CUSTOM_SQL
column.value:
SELECT COUNT (*) AS Y, REPLACE(COALESCE (P.PARAM_VALUE, ''),'_',' ') AS X FROM STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS P INNER JOIN STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS W ON P.ENTITY_ID = W.ENTITY_ID AND W.PARAM_NAME = 'Wave' AND W.PARAM_VALUE = 1
WHERE P.PARAM_NAME = 'Migration_Status' AND P.PARAM_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND P.PARAM_VALUE != ''
GROUP BY P.PARAM_VALUE ORDER BY 1

column.name: CUSTOM_SQL
column.value:
SELECT COUNT (*) AS Y, REPLACE(COALESCE (P.PARAM_VALUE, ''),'_',' ') AS X FROM STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS P INNER JOIN STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS W ON P.ENTITY_ID = W.ENTITY_ID AND W.PARAM_NAME = 'Migration_Status' AND W.PARAM_VALUE = 'Identifying'
WHERE P.PARAM_NAME = 'Wave' AND P.PARAM_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND P.PARAM_VALUE != ''
GROUP BY P.PARAM_VALUE ORDER BY 2 ASC

column.name: CUSTOM_SQL
column.value:
SELECT COUNT (*) AS Y, REPLACE(COALESCE (P.PARAM_VALUE, ''),'_',' ') AS X FROM STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS P INNER JOIN STAGE_ENTITY_PARAMS W ON P.ENTITY_ID = W.ENTITY_ID AND W.PARAM_NAME = 'Migration_Status' AND W.PARAM_VALUE = 'Completed'
WHERE P.PARAM_NAME = 'Wave' AND P.PARAM_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND P.PARAM_VALUE != ''
GROUP BY P.PARAM_VALUE ORDER BY 2 ASC
